Physical strength was at the heart
of the village.

103
00:07:19,519 --> 00:07:21,839
The guy who had no consideration at all

104
00:07:21,919 --> 00:07:23,119
was the guy who was lazy.

105
00:07:27,639 --> 00:07:30,039
Very, very strong Catholic region.

106
00:07:31,919 --> 00:07:34,319
We had to go to the Mass,
we had to confess.

107
00:07:35,799 --> 00:07:37,639
I learned that at a very young age.

108
00:07:40,279 --> 00:07:46,159
WENGER IN FRENCH:

109
00:07:55,159 --> 00:07:57,999
BELL TOLLS

110
00:07:59,599 --> 00:08:02,919
My first memories, the church,
the football pitch

111
00:08:02,999 --> 00:08:04,759
and the restaurant
where I grew up.

112
00:08:07,039 --> 00:08:09,599
My father was an accountant
at Bugatti.

113
00:08:10,599 --> 00:08:13,439
My mother had inherited this bar.

114
00:08:15,159 --> 00:08:17,479
It was one of the three
or four in the village

115
00:08:17,559 --> 00:08:20,839
