138
00:11:13,839 --> 00:11:16,999
WENGER: I could sense
that the team was looking at me

139
00:11:17,559 --> 00:11:20,359
thinking, "What is this guy?
What is he doing here?"

140
00:11:20,719 --> 00:11:22,119
How can I sum him up?

141
00:11:22,999 --> 00:11:24,359
What can I say?

142
00:11:26,119 --> 00:11:27,879
He had a massive jacket on

143
00:11:28,519 --> 00:11:29,759
glasses were massive.

144
00:11:31,199 --> 00:11:32,559
My nickname for him was "Clueso".

145
00:11:32,959 --> 00:11:34,879
It is Chief Inspector...

146
00:11:36,039 --> 00:11:37,199
Clueso.

147
00:11:37,279 --> 00:11:39,439
Pink Panther! We was watching
a lot of Pink Panther.

148
00:11:39,519 --> 00:11:40,639
Please come in.

149
00:11:41,239 --> 00:11:42,639
So many cameras here...

150
00:11:43,439 --> 00:11:45,279
I feel like I'm making a movie.

151
00:11:45,359 --> 00:11:46,439
WRIGHT:
He would trip up

152
00:11:47,319 --> 00:11:48,399
