00:11:55,279 --> 00:11:56,239
Sorry, my friend.

157
00:11:58,719 --> 00:12:01,159
WRIGHT: There was a time
when we played against Wimbledon...

158
00:12:01,599 --> 00:12:03,559
the lights went off,
so we were walking back in

159
00:12:03,759 --> 00:12:05,879
and as we were walking back in,
he was getting ready to come out

160
00:12:05,959 --> 00:12:07,559
and he said, "What's going on?"

161
00:12:08,319 --> 00:12:10,759
Honestly, we went,
"There's a burmb."

162
00:12:11,079 --> 00:12:13,399
And he went, "A burmb?"
HE LAUGHS

163
00:12:13,479 --> 00:12:14,679
A burmb!

